('How to redirect to custom 404 page in Remix', 'backend', 'MEDIUM', '[{"solution": "In loader, throw new Response(\"Not found\", {status: 404}) to trigger CatchBoundary", "percentage": 90}, {"solution": "Export CatchBoundary component in root.tsx to display custom 404", "percentage": 88}, {"solution": "Use splat route $.tsx to catch unmatched URLs", "percentage": 85}]'::jsonb, 'Remix CatchBoundary, routing', 'Custom 404 page displays for invalid routes', 'Using redirect() instead of throw Response, missing CatchBoundary export', 0.87, 'haiku', NOW(), 'https://stackoverflow.com/questions/74060186/how-to-redirect-to-a-custom-404-page-in-remix-run', 'admin:1764224696'),

